OL,5, Ministers will consider advice from the
OL,6, human rights watchdog about amending a 
OL,7, legal definition of sex - which would  
OL,8, make it easier to exclude transgender  
OL,9, people from some groups or services.   
OL,11,FChanging the Equality Act term to      
OL,12,F"biological sex" would make single-sex 
OL,13,Fservices offers easier, says the EHRC  
OL,14,F(Equality and Human Rights Commission).
OL,16,FLGBTQ+ charity Stonewall said it risks 
OL,17,Fadding to a "manufactured culture war".
OL,19,FThe EHRC says it would give clarity in 
OL,20,Fa "polarised and contentious" area.    
